lead_paragraph: Many expected France coach Didier Deschamps would be grumpy at a news conference the day before Sunday's European Championship quarter-final against Iceland, having had to travel all the way from his team's base to the Stade de France.

headline.print_headline: Happy France Coach Wings In to Face the Press
